      • Card

        public Card​(java.lang.String newName,
            int newBlood,
            int newHealth,
            int newAttack)
        Constructs new card using the assigned values from the start. These can be read from a file. I called the setters here in case we desire to regulate these values more heavily later on.
        Parameters:
        newName - Name of the card.
        newHealth - Amount of health.
        newAttack - Amount of Attack.
        newBlood - Amount of blood which it costs to put card into play.
